              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Yes. Lower competition means newer or smaller sites with limited domain authority can reach page one within weeks for long-tail targets, while the same sites might need years to rank for head terms. The tradeoff is lower individual search volume per keyword.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
