            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Research consistently shows long-tail keyword conversion rates running 2-5x higher than head terms. The reason is specificity of intent: a searcher typing a 6-word query has already refined their thinking and is much closer to a decision than someone searching a broad 1-2 word term.</p></div></div>
